{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f04eb911be","title":"江青给国防科委情报资料研究所恽仁祥的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9b034b01da","index":0,"year":1974,"month":2,"day":10,"articleId":"f04eb911be"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"ff3246377b","name":"批陈整风和批林批孔","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"/books/jqjianghua.pdf"},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1762134a77","type":"title","text":"江青给国防科委情报资料研究所恽仁祥的信","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"9ec0b0722d","type":"appellation","text":"恽仁祥同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"13dbf7a20c","type":"paragraph","text":"你一九七四年一月三十一日的信，我今天早上才收到。我很抱歉，未能及时收到你的信。","index":2,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"2ddeea9434","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的材料那么困难，我很惊讶！国防科委的批林批孔运动搞不起来，必有原因，得你们自己找。我相信只要按毛主席的教导去做，总会冲破障碍而前进的。道路是曲折的，前途是光明的！","index":3,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"2c7dca49ee","type":"appellation","text":"现送上：","index":4,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"0bfeae8691","type":"paragraph","text":"《林彪与孔孟之道》","index":5,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"7c223fe342","type":"paragraph","text":"《五四以来反动派、地主资产阶级学者尊孔复古言论辑录》","index":6,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"7e5b3c71cf","type":"paragraph","text":"《批林批孔文章汇编》（一）（二）","index":7,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"97ba0ecdb4","type":"paragraph","text":"以上材料各 100份。如不足，我可以再送，请告我数字。","index":8,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"6f07c27e7c","type":"paragraph","text":"这封信可以给国防科委所有愿意参加批林批孔的同志看。不愿参加批林批孔的人要，也可以看。","index":9,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"f6298ac3fa","type":"paragraph","text":"不要再闹资产阶级派性了，敌人利用派性挑拨离间，要在马列主义、毛泽东思想的原则基础上团结起来！批林批孔是路线斗争，要抓住批林批孔路线斗争这个纲，这就是目前我国党、政、军、民、学以及其他各界的头等大事。","index":10,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"5c201d3765","type":"paragraph","text":"胜利是会属于用马列主义、毛泽东思想武装起来的同志们！","index":11,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"54ebe01d9f","type":"paragraph","text":"致以","index":12,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"96b6b31d5f","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级的革命的敬礼！","index":13,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"83df950901","type":"paragraph","text":"江青一九七四．二．十．晨","index":14,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be"}],"page":{"id":"3705613de4","publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"f04eb911be","start":689,"end":689}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"330322bdb7","type":"paragraph","text":"现送上：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"342710b69e","type":"paragraph","text":"你一九七四年一月三十一日的信，我今天早上才收到。我很抱歉，未能及时收到你的信。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"3b927a252c","type":"paragraph","text":"恽仁祥同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"4feff09bbe","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的材料那么困难，我很惊讶！国防科委的批林批孔运动搞不起来，必有原因，得你们自己找。我相信只要按毛主席的教导去做，总会冲破障碍而前进的。道路是曲折的，前途是光明的！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"5c0378617e","type":"paragraph","text":"胜利是会属于用马列主义、毛泽东思想武装起来的同志们！","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"5fd98a7d41","type":"paragraph","text":"致以","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"7913a1c126","type":"paragraph","text":"江青","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f04eb911be"},{"id":"7a6c0e25f2","type":"paragraph"